videos.description: Danielle Rauch shows off with a beautiful overhead hook pass to Laila Phelia who quickly pulls up for a Michigan 3-pointer.

videos.description: Elise Stuck sends a nice bounce pass ahead to Naz Hillmon, who uses her body to get by the Maryland defense and to the hoop for a bucket plus the foul.
